You told me you turned it in.

02:42.011 --> 02:43.645
How am I not
the account holder

02:43.680 --> 02:45.147
if my name is on the bill?

02:45.181 --> 02:47.399
N-No, don't put me...

02:47.433 --> 02:49.234
I gave it to the teacher,
the guy with the...

02:49.269 --> 02:50.652
thing on his head...
I'll call him.

02:50.687 --> 02:51.687
You can't call.

02:51.738 --> 02:53.322
They had to be
cleared last week.

02:53.356 --> 02:56.074
And I'm sorry, I'll take you
to museum myself... how's that?

02:56.109 --> 02:58.026
It's not about the museum.
It's about the fact that

02:58.077 --> 02:59.995
now I have to spend
the day in study hall

03:00.029 --> 03:02.080
because you didn't turn in a
simple piece of paper.

03:02.115 --> 03:03.699
I'm telling you,
I'm pretty sure I gave...

03:03.750 --> 03:05.650
the guy something, unless
I gave him the phone bill.

03:05.668 --> 03:07.085
Well, no, no, no.

03:07.120 --> 03:08.587
I'm talking to my son.
Don't, don't...

03:08.621 --> 03:10.789
Listen, how could it
take you three days

03:10.823 --> 03:12.341
to switch the service back on

03:12.375 --> 03:14.092
when you have my money today?

03:14.127 --> 03:15.327
Hold on a second.

03:15.345 --> 03:17.346
Yeah?

03:17.380 --> 03:19.181
I'm on my way.

03:19.215 --> 03:21.166
Hello?

03:21.184 --> 03:23.268
Hello?

03:25.104 --> 03:26.638
All right.
You ready to go?

03:26.672 --> 03:28.974
I told you yesterday,
Cole's dad is taking me.

03:29.008 --> 03:31.509
- I'll text you when I'm out.
- No, you won't.

03:31.527 --> 03:34.012
Your phone's not gonna
be on for three days.

03:34.030 --> 03:35.681
What?!

03:35.715 --> 03:37.866
It's gonna be back on
on Wednesday.

03:37.901 --> 03:39.952
The phone company
messed up. I'm sorry.

